### Show Model Status and Auth Overview

Source: https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/blob/main/docs/concepts/models.md

Displays the resolved primary model, fallbacks, image model, and an authentication overview of configured providers. It also shows OAuth expiry status and warns if credentials are missing. Use `--plain` for only the primary model and `--check` for automation.

```bash
claude setup-token
openclaw models status
```

