### Switching Models via Slash Commands

Source: https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/blob/main/docs/help/faq.md

Demonstrates how to quickly switch between different AI models for specific tasks using slash commands. This is useful for session-specific model changes.

```shell
/model gpt-5.2
/model gpt-5.2-codex
```
